	"description":"The Post-Anarchist Canis Kollective is what survived when the hidden societies of Canis stopped merely rejecting authority and began building a future in public. P.A.C.K. doctrine favors mixed hull groups, support craft, escorts, and stubborn communal coordination over imperial line warfare. They are diplomatic by necessity, suspicious by history, and fiercely protective of the Exodus that brought them out from Petra's poisoned sky.",
